{"tid":437445,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"要任陪審員員工周六上班 法官下令衞生署署長出庭解釋","createTime":"2017-10-16T04:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-16T04:54:36.000Z","uid":72009,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"910c47be31d0c75f9e04db8a339349188ef40d10","tid":437445,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:12:14.000Z","msg":"前特首曾蔭權被指於在任期間接受豪華裝修工程，被控行政長官收受利益罪一案，今早甫開庭，法官透露上周五收到衞生署的傳真，要求本案其中於署方工作的陪審員周六上班，法官決定要求衞生署署長陳漢儀今日下午4:00到法庭解釋。<br />\n<br />\n法官早於抽選陪審員時已表明，任陪審員是公民責任，審訊中途亦已告知陪審員，僱主不能要求他們在周六上班。<br />\n<br />\n法官向陪審團表示，相信他們知道為何遲開庭，並告知已要求衞生署署長今日到法庭解釋，他們將會知道答案，然後提醒他們繼續專心聽審。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等睇道歉"},{"pid":"3b70679d1293f3e6de5f62d45ab7955f137db19b","tid":437445,"uid":55846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  政府部門都咁"},{"pid":"bef657a4ac5c22075dd78019b97482cdd3e2d474","tid":437445,"uid":139107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:38:51.000Z","msg":"政府部門私鬥<br />\n好睇過曹星如"},{"pid":"fd1152530cf4f040ec682141d6e173d6224d2cc8","tid":437445,"uid":71345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:39:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a656ca2aba20223c045c075a025d9039128cf43c","tid":437445,"uid":32114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:53:49.000Z","msg":"留名等睇法庭通緝衛生署署長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"771db842416a12fb6c66fefe0756f0332e5009db","tid":437445,"uid":40779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-16T04:54:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名等睇法庭通緝衛生署署長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></b